column2: "Thanks for waiting everyone!"

"I’ll go at maximum speed today!
Make sure you keep up with me!"

"Transcend through the marvellous galaxies!
Let’s shine like the stars, everyone!
『Cosmic twinkle star』!"
"Cosmic parades fluctuating space"

"Stars' reincarnation over
tens of millions of light years"

"Gliding from the past to the future
like a shining jet coaster"
"How much hope can it carry aboard?"

"When I looked up, I stopped and
realised that nothing will start"
"Our infinite world is still waiting for us"

"Let’s go towards the twinkle star
shining within the galaxies"
"Twinkling every moment, over and over again"

"Let the future song echo
far beyond the horizon"
"It’s a big scale adventure"
"Let’s all fly together!"
"Flashing sky hiding the unknown stage"

"A mysterious destination
with scattering jewels"
"The hologram scenery spins the stardust merry-go-round"
"Towards the unsophisticated vortex"
"Don’t look behind when you’re confused"

"Tomorrow will always shine a
light right before your eyes"

"Galaxies carrying that twinkle star,
light up our dreams"
"To grasp a hold onto our number one wish"

"Let the future song
bring you even further"
"To this spectacular planet"
"And embrace it’s beauty"

"Let’s go towards the twinkle star
shining within the galaxies"
"Twinkling every moment, over and over again"

"Let the future song echo
far beyond the horizon"
"It’s a big scale adventure"
"Let’s all fly together!"

"Galaxies carrying that twinkle star,
light up our dreams"
"To grasp a hold onto our number one wish"

"Let the future song
bring you even further"
"To this spectacular planet"
"and embrace it’s beauty"
"Both our songs"
"Will become the miracle of light in our universe"
"Cosmic twinkle star"
"Quna"
